h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-57b1de0 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"57b1de0\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-69e48b1 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"69e48b1\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-74ee849 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget-mobile__width-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"74ee849\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Our Tee Fitting and Reducing Tee Fitting are indispensable components in fluid conveyance systems, adept at creating branch connections and accommodating changes in pipe diameter with precision and reliability. Engineered with meticulous detail and forged from high-grade materials, these fittings ensure seamless fluid distribution in piping networks across diverse industries.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-cc3eb5a animated-slow elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"cc3eb5a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;fadeInUp&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Key Features<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d1d81ad e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"d1d81ad\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-03690c3 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"03690c3\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3daba9d elementor-widget__width-